	<li>Official website of Industry Design department, Zhejiang University. I am the only front end web developer. Demo can be viewed <a title="External: http://zjuid.sinaapp.com/" href="http://zjuid.sinaapp.com/" target="_blank">here</a>.</li>
	<li><a title="External: http://musicgarden.coding.io/" href="http://musicgarden.coding.io/" target="_blank">Music Garden</a>. A music assets management website initially intended for the Digital Asset Management course. Developed independently. Refer to <a title="External: http://shuailong.github.io/MusicGarden/" href="http://shuailong.github.io/MusicGarden/" target="_balnk">here</a> for project introduction page.</li>
