	<li>Crazy Express. Game Design course final projects. Exhibited on Digital Media Openday. Screenshots can be viewed <a title="Internal: http://shuailong.me/game.html" href="http://shuailong.me/game.html" target="_blank">here</a>. Game models can be viewed <a title="Internal: http://shuailong.me/model.html" href="http://shuailong.me/model.html" target="_blank">here</a>.</li>
	<li><a title="External: http://watermark.coding.io/" href="http://watermark.coding.io/" target="_blank">Image Watermarking</a>. A convenience online tool to add your customized watermark to your copyrighted images. Developed independently. Refer to <a title="External: http://shuailong.github.io/ImageWatermarking/" href="http://shuailong.github.io/ImageWatermarking/" target="_blank">here</a> for project introduction page.</li>
